file.name: dox.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: tstdox
  version: 1.0.1
servers:
  - url: /tstdox
paths:
  /iface/funA:
    post:
      tags:
        - iface
      summary: comment for funA of MyIface
      description: "detailed description for funA of MyIface\n\nwarning for funA of MyIface"
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyIface.funAArgs"
      responses:
        '200':
          description: RPC success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyIface.funARes"
        '500':
          description: "local comment for MyIface.funA.throw\n\ncomment for funA.throw"
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyStruct"
        default:
          description: generic error
          content:
            text/html:
              schema:
                type: string
  /iface/funAa:
    post:
      tags:
        - iface
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyIface.funAaArgs"
      responses:
        '200':
          description: RPC success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyIface.funAaRes"
        default:
          description: generic error
          content:
            text/html:
              schema:
                type: string
  /iface/funB:
    post:
      tags:
        - iface
      summary: comment for MyIface.funB
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyIface.funBArgs"
      responses:
        '200':
          description: comment for MyIface.funB.out
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyUnion"
        default:
          description: generic error
          content:
            text/html:
              schema:
                type: string
  /iface/funBal1:
    post:
      tags:
        - iface
      summary: comment for MyIface.funB
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyIface.funBal1Args"
      responses:
        '200':
          description: comment for MyIface.funB.out
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyUnion"
        default:
          description: generic error
          content:
            text/html:
              schema:
                type: string
  /iface/funBal2:
    post:
      tags:
        - iface
      summary: comment for MyIface.funB
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyIface.funBal2Args"
      responses:
        '200':
          description: comment for MyIface.funB.out
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyUnion"
        default:
          description: generic error
          content:
            text/html:
              schema:
                type: string
  /iface/funC:
    post:
      tags:
        - iface
      summary: comment for MyIface.funC
      requestBody:
        required: true
        description: comment for MyIface.funC.in
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyStruct"
      responses:
        '200':
          description: RPC success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyIface.funCRes"
        default:
          description: generic error
          content:
            text/html:
              schema:
                type: string
  /iface/funD:
    post:
      tags:
        - iface
      summary: front comment... and back comment for funD
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Void"
      responses:
        '200':
          description: RPC success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyIface.funDRes"
        default:
          description: generic error
          content:
            text/html:
              schema:
                type: string
  /iface/funE:
    post:
      tags:
        - iface
      summary: Comment for funE
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyIface.funEArgs"
      responses:
        '200':
          description: RPC success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Void"
        default:
          description: generic error
          content:
            text/html:
              schema:
                type: string
  /iface/funE1:
    post:
      tags:
        - iface
      summary: Comment for funE
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyIface.funE1Args"
      responses:
        '200':
          description: RPC success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Void"
        default:
          description: generic error
          content:
            text/html:
              schema:
                type: string
  /iface/funE2:
    post:
      tags:
        - iface
      summary: Comment for funE
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyIface.funE2Args"
      responses:
        '200':
          description: RPC success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Void"
        default:
          description: generic error
          content:
            text/html:
              schema:
                type: string
components:
  schemas:
    tstiop_dox.MyEnum:
      type: string
      description: "comment for MyEnum\n\ndetails for MyEnum \\word not a recognized keyword\n\nwarn for MyEnum"
      enum:
        - VAL_A
        - VAL_B
        - VAL_C
    tstiop_dox.MyStruct:
      type: object
      description: comment for MyStruct
      required:
        - fieldA
        - fieldB
        - fieldC
      properties:
        fieldA:
          type: integer
          format: int32
          description: comment for MyStruct.fieldA
        fieldB:
          $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyEnum"
        fieldC:
          type: integer
          format: int32
          description: comment for MyStruct.fieldC
    tstiop_dox.MyIface.funAArgs:
      type: object
      description: local comment for MyIface.funA.in
      required:
        - aParam
        - b
      properties:
        aParam:
          type: integer
          format: int32
          description: "local comment for MyIface.funA.in.aParam\n\ncomment for aParam of funA.in\n                      it continues here"
        b:
          description: "local comment for MyIface.funA.in.b\n\ncomment for b of funA.in"
          allOf:
            - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyStruct"
      example: "{\"aParam\":1,\"b\":{\"fieldA\":11,\"fieldB\":12,\"fieldC\":13}}"
    tstiop_dox.MyClass:
      type: object
      properties:
        _class:
          type: string
      discriminator:
        propertyName: _class
    tstiop_dox.MyClassChild:
      allOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyClass"
        - type: object
    tstiop_dox.MyIface.funARes:
      type: object
      description: local comment for MyIface.funA.out
      required:
        - d
      properties:
        c:
          description: "local comment for MyIface.funA.out.c\n\ncomment for c of funA.out"
          oneOf:
            - $ref: "#/components/schemas/tstiop_dox.MyClassChild"
          discriminator:
            propertyName: _class
        d:
          type: integer
          format: int32
          description: "comment for \\ref d of funA.out\n2nd paragraph for \\p d of funA.out"
      example: "{\"c\":{\"_class\":\"tstiop_dox.MyClassChild\"},\"d\":4}"
    tstiop_dox.MyIface.funAaArgs:
      type: object
      description: comment for MyIface.funAa.in
      required:
        - a
      properties:
        a:
          type: integer
          format: int32
    tstiop_dox.MyIface.funAaRes:
      type: object
      required:
        - b
      properties:
        b:
          type: integer
          format: int32
      example: "{\"b\":3}"
    tstiop_dox.MyIface.funBArgs:
      type: object
      description: comment for MyIface.funB.in
      required:
        - a
      properties:
        a:
          type: integer
          format: int32
    tstiop_dox.MyUnion:
      description: comment for MyUnion
      oneOf:
        - type: object
          required:
            - fieldA
          properties:
            fieldA:
              type: boolean
              description: comment for MyUnion.fieldA
        - type: object
          required:
            - fieldB
          properties:
            fieldB:
              type: boolean
    tstiop_dox.MyIface.funBal1Args:
      type: object
      description: comment for MyIface.funB.in
      required:
        - a
      properties:
        a:
          type: integer
          format: int32
    tstiop_dox.MyIface.funBal2Args:
      type: object
      description: comment for MyIface.funB.in
      required:
        - a
      properties:
        a:
          type: integer
          format: int32
    tstiop_dox.MyIface.funCRes:
      type: object
      required:
        - b
      properties:
        b:
          type: integer
          format: int32
    Void:
      type: object
    tstiop_dox.MyIface.funDRes:
      type: object
      description: front comment... and back comment for res of funD
      required:
        - b
      properties:
        b:
          type: integer
          format: int32
    tstiop_dox.MyIface.funEArgs:
      type: object
      required:
        - a
      properties:
        a:
          type: integer
          format: int32
          description: It is a \p comment for \ref a
    tstiop_dox.MyIface.funE1Args:
      type: object
      required:
        - a
      properties:
        a:
          type: integer
          format: int32
          description: It is a \p comment for \ref a
    tstiop_dox.MyIface.funE2Args:
      type: object
      required:
        - a
      properties:
        a:
          type: integer
          format: int32
          description: It is a \p comment for \ref a
tags:
  - name: iface
    description: "comment for MyModule.iface\n\ncomment for MyIface"
